00:18:27,239 --> 00:18:28,608
I managed to weigh 65kg.

488
00:18:28,674 --> 00:18:29,809
- Without eating carbohydrates?
- Yes.

489
00:18:29,875 --> 00:18:33,412
I read an article on Money Today
on April 28, 2025.

490
00:18:33,479 --> 00:18:34,914
- All of a sudden?
- You surprised me.

491
00:18:34,981 --> 00:18:37,917
- Hang on. You sound really scary.
- You surprised me.

492
00:18:37,984 --> 00:18:39,819
It sounds like a line
from <i>Unanswered Questions.</i>

493
00:18:39,885 --> 00:18:42,588
It says Joo Won was such a bit eater
when he was young

494
00:18:42,755 --> 00:18:44,790
that he would eat 40 hamburgers at a time.

495
00:18:45,591 --> 00:18:46,559
JOO WON IS THE GRANDSON
OF A FAMOUS CHINESE RESTAURANT OWNER

496
00:18:46,626 --> 00:18:47,727
HE ATE 40 HAMBURGERS IN MIDDLE SCHOOL

497
00:18:47,793 --> 00:18:48,728
Is that true?

498
00:18:48,794 --> 00:18:50,596
- That can't be true.
- Hey, 40 hamburgers...

499
00:18:50,663 --> 00:18:52,264
- That's impossible.
- You were probably exaggerating.

500
00:18:52,331 --> 00:18:53,766
How can a person eat 40 hamburgers?

501
00:18:54,033 --> 00:18:56,569
- I think the article is incorrect.
- Really?

502
00:18:56,636 --> 00:18:57,870
- I knew it.
- Actually,

503
00:18:57,937 --> 00:18:58,971
I ate 20 hamburgers.

504
00:18:59,839 --> 00:19:00,840
Twenty...

505
00:19:02,575 --> 00:19:04,076
- Twenty...
- Twenty burgers are still a lot.

506
00:19:04,143 --> 00:19:05,911
- Did you really eat 20 hamburgers?
- I did.

507
00:19:05,978 --> 00:19:08,381
I think this is why they said 40 burgers.

508
00:19:08,447 --> 00:19:10,216
Back then, my brother and I ate
40 burgers in total.

509
00:19:10,616 --> 00:19:12,184
- We ate 20 burgers each.
- Did your brother eat 20 burgers too?

510
00:19:12,251 --> 00:19:13,352
Yes, he did.

511
00:19:14,553 --> 00:19:16,622
It was back in my teens
when I had a big appetite.

512
00:19:16,689 --> 00:19:18,224
I wanted to eat hamburgers,

513
00:19:18,290 --> 00:19:19,759
and I wanted to eat a lot.

514
00:19:19,825 --> 00:19:22,795
Back then, a hamburger brand had
burgers that were only 1,000 won each.

515
00:19:23,462 --> 00:19:25,631
- I know what it is.
- I know.

516
00:19:25,698 --> 00:19:28,567
It was a simple burger,
only with a bun and a patty.

517
00:19:28,634 --> 00:19:30,169
- Exactly. Only a bun and a patty.
- Right.

518
00:19:30,236 --> 00:19:32,938
My brother and I each ordered
20 of those and ate them.

519
00:19:34,106 --> 00:19:35,241
You were a huge eater.

520
00:19:35,307 --> 00:19:38,010
There are a few things I've quit
since my TV debut.

521
00:19:38,077 --> 00:19:39,412
- What?
- Eating spicy food.

522
00:19:39,645 --> 00:19:41,380
I don't eat spicy food.

523
00:19:41,447 --> 00:19:43,849
- For real?
- And I stopped eating rice.

524
00:19:43,983 --> 00:19:46,719
So, you don't eat those things
even when you eat with your lover?

525
00:19:47,286 --> 00:19:48,220
With my lover?

526
00:19:48,287 --> 00:19:49,221
- Yes.
- I'm curious.

527
00:19:50,723 --> 00:19:51,757
I should eat.

528
00:19:51,824 --> 00:19:54,660
So, what's the situation now?

529
00:19:55,227 --> 00:19:56,195
What do you mean?

530
00:19:56,295 --> 00:20:00,232
If your girlfriend wants to eat them,
do you eat with her?

531
00:20:03,002 --> 00:20:04,103
- Now?
- Yes.

532
00:20:09,942 --> 00:20:11,010
- Now?
- Yes.

533
00:20:11,177 --> 00:20:12,778
- I can't do that now.
- Why not?

534
00:20:13,045 --> 00:20:14,580
- I mean...
- Because I don't have a girlfriend.

535
00:20:15,147 --> 00:20:16,182
- You don't?
- No.

536
00:20:17,016 --> 00:20:18,617
- He doesn't.
- You're lying!

537
00:20:18,684 --> 00:20:19,618
Really?

538
00:20:19,985 --> 00:20:22,021
Why are you guys making a fuss?

539
00:20:22,088 --> 00:20:23,055
Breathless!

540
00:20:23,122 --> 00:20:24,824
- Ballet!
- Ballet!

541
00:20:25,224 --> 00:20:26,425
You're all too much.

542
00:20:26,959 --> 00:20:29,228
So, let's say there's a scene in a film

543
00:20:29,295 --> 00:20:31,664
