and says this.

545
00:20:33,933 --> 00:20:36,168
- "Joo Won, I'm not very good at cooking,
- Yes?

546
00:20:36,469 --> 00:20:39,371
- but I made a homemade burger for you."
- I'm curious.

547
00:20:40,673 --> 00:20:43,209
- I'm curious.
- "Eat this, and good luck tomorrow."

548
00:20:43,275 --> 00:20:44,677
