551
00:20:49,548 --> 00:20:51,517
- Enjoy it.
- Hear me out.

552
00:20:52,251 --> 00:20:55,321
I haven't even had water since yesterday,

553
00:20:55,721 --> 00:20:57,389
and tomorrow,

554
00:20:57,623 --> 00:20:59,792
I have a scene where I have to be topless.

555
00:21:00,292 --> 00:21:03,496
So, I'll keep this and eat it
