558
00:21:08,467 --> 00:21:10,336
Wouldn't it be better that way?

559
00:21:10,402 --> 00:21:12,705
- It's so sad.
- But I just wanted you

560
00:21:12,772 --> 00:21:15,174
to eat something I just made.

561
00:21:16,642 --> 00:21:17,977
You're a piece of sxxx
if you don't eat it.

562
00:21:22,081 --> 00:21:23,616
Where are you going?

563
00:21:24,150 --> 00:21:26,919
- Joo Won, where are you going?
- He's leaving.

564
00:21:28,587 --> 00:21:29,955
