even if I don't want to go.

591
00:22:24,476 --> 00:22:26,979
When I go and exercise,
my headache goes away.

592
00:22:27,046 --> 00:22:29,215
You're so determined.

593
00:22:29,381 --> 00:22:31,417
Right. That's incredible.

594
00:22:31,851 --> 00:22:33,619
- You don't even drink.
- I almost forgot.

595
00:22:33,686 --> 00:22:35,387
Min, you know the thing we got
