669
00:25:04,603 --> 00:25:05,804
Behave yourself!

670
00:25:07,272 --> 00:25:08,974
I wanted to wear them.

671
00:25:09,041 --> 00:25:10,476
I wanted to wear them.

672
00:25:10,542 --> 00:25:12,211
- That's why I started ballet.
