What kind of rules? You agree, right?

698
00:26:08,300 --> 00:26:09,401
Yes. We need some rules.

699
00:26:09,468 --> 00:26:11,036
Of course, we do.

700
00:26:12,538 --> 00:26:15,040
Then Ye-eun should wear neutral colors

701
00:26:15,107 --> 00:26:16,975
- and take off her necklace.
- But I think

702
00:26:17,409 --> 00:26:19,244
