Why don't we try that thing
we did earlier, the lift, one more time?

1073
00:40:49,347 --> 00:40:50,548
- Let's do that.
- Good idea.

1074
00:40:50,615 --> 00:40:51,816
All right. Finish your fried chicken.

1075
00:40:51,883 --> 00:40:54,152
- Two people can do it.
- All right.

1076
00:40:54,218 --> 00:40:55,420
- That's enough.
- Come on.

1077
00:40:55,486 --> 00:40:57,188
<i>- We need to eat.</i>
<i>- This is nice.</i>

1078
00:40:57,255 --> 00:40:58,122
<i>That's enough.</i>

1079
